مَاء : water : 13*

عَنْ : about/concerning : 13

مَعَ : with : 13

إلى : to/towards : 13

مَلَكِيّ : royal : 13

أَمْس : yesterday : 13*

صَبَاح : morning : 13

مَسَاء : afternoon/evening : 13

مَتى؟ : when? : 13 : Compare مَا‎ (mā, “what?”) and مَن‎ (man, “who?”). Cognate to Hebrew מתי‎ (matai) "when".

مَاذا؟ : what? (for verbal sentences) : 13 : See note on p. 174. Example "ماذا فعل الملك أمس؟" ("What did the king do yesterday?"). Interrogative pronoun. WK\: "The simple form ما‎ is used only in nominal sentences, while the extended form ماذا is used in verbal sentences."

مَاذَا تُرِيدَ? : What would you like? : 13+ : Example use of مَاذَا. 

